        "text_cBDBzK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every product begins with the materials. We choose fabrics that meet our performance standards while avoiding harmful chemistry and unnecessary impact. When the right fabric doesn’t exist, we develop it.</p><p>Designing for durability, both in performance and in style, is one of the most sustainable choices we can make, and we consider cost per wear from the start. We prioritize bluesign®-approved fabrics, use PFAS-free DWR, and give unused materials a second life through our <a href=\"/pages/fabric-story-polartec\" title=\"Fabric Story: Polartec\">Special Projects</a> collection.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
