        },
        "text_GCcpKy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Great products are made all over the world, but we produce as much as possible here in the U.S., with nearly everything sewn in the Bay Area. Close proximity lets us work directly with our sewing partners, maintain quality, and operate responsibly, with clear communication and shared accountability at every step.</p><p>Domestic production reduces emissions, supports skilled jobs, and keeps value circulating in the local economy. It’s more complex and often more expensive than producing overseas, but for us, it’s the right choice.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
